In our increasingly cramped urban lives, it&rsquo;s obligatory to occasionally roam the vast expanse of the countryside and reconnect with nature&rsquo;s tranquility. As the old proverb goes, &ldquo;The apprehensive mind grows wings in the wilderness.&rdquo;
在我们越来越狭窄的城市生活中，有时有必要去漫游乡村的广袤天地，重新与自然的宁静联系起来。正如古老的谚语所说：“忧虑的心在旷野中生出翅膀。”
Last summer, I embarked on a solo hiking adventure, seeking an asylum from the raucous city life. The trail wound through a barren landscape, but soon I stumbled upon a lush meadow adorned with vibrant wildflowers and sprouting saplings.
